	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad priores literas<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Nicht erhalten.</note> respondebo, charissime frater, ubi moderationem tuam in praedestinationis causa<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Gemeint ist Bullingers Karlstagsrede vom 28. Januar 1535 "Quae moderatio servanda sit..." (vgl. unten <ref target="file10630">Nr. 592</ref> mit Anm. 2).</note> remisero, quod brevi fiet<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwick</persName> sandte Bullingers Schrift am 3. Juli zurück, vgl. unten <ref target="file10646">Nr. 608</ref>, 1-11.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Relegit <persName ref="p8178" cert="high">Thomas</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8178" cert="high">Thomas Blarer</persName> nahm schon am 16. Juni Stellung, s. unten <ref target="file10630">Nr. 592</ref>.</note>, iam in manu est fratris<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p4082" cert="high">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note>, deinde in meam quoque recipiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In posterioribus literis<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Nicht erhalten; vgl. oben <ref target="file10623">Nr. 585</ref>, 22-31.</note> summe placent, quae <persName ref="p2840" cert="high">Alexandrum</persName><note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="p2840" cert="high">Alexander Schmutz</persName>.</note> adtinent.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego, cum nuper ex <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> rediisset, vici coram fratribus omniaque argumenta fregi homini.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">An obtemperaturus sit, nescio, sed nihil sum praetermissurus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam pessime odi desertiones ecclesiarum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De aliis proxime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">O wie denck ich so offt dran, wie wir so guͦt leben ghept hond zuͦ <placeName ref="l515" cert="high">Urdorf</placeName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Zu <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Zwicks</persName> Badeaufenthalt in <placeName ref="l515" cert="high">Urdorf</placeName> (Kt. Zürich) vgl. oben <ref target="file10610">Nr. 572</ref>, Anm. 37.</note> Es wurt mir min lebenlang nymer als<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">so.</note> guͦt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Grutzen mir uwer husfrowen<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="p8051" cert="high">Anna Bullinger, geb. Adlischwyler</persName>.</note> und die muͦter<note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="p7042" cert="high">Anna Bullinger, geb. Wiederkehr</persName>.</note> 1, ja yederman.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Und sye got mit uch allen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">5. iunii 1535.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Io. Z. tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. Hainricho Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae antistiti dignissimo, fratri suo bene meritissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
